1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 13=

4
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:22,280
Master.

5
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:23,480
Ready?

6
00:00:23,679 --> 00:00:24,199
Let's do this.

7
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:42,719
Spicy! Spicy!

8
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:43,840
But Changsheng,

9
00:00:44,079 --> 00:00:46,200
hot pot has to be extra spicy
with beef tallow.

10
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:47,119
That's what makes it so good.

11
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:48,520
Master,

12
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:50,719
if word gets out
that I used treating you

13
00:00:50,719 --> 00:00:52,159
as an excuse to feast in here,

14
00:00:52,159 --> 00:00:54,799
my reputation as the Divine Healer

15
00:00:54,799 --> 00:00:56,000
will be ruined for good.

16
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:58,280
Still, with food this good, who cares?

17
00:00:58,719 --> 00:01:00,359
With my master's pills,

18
00:01:00,359 --> 00:01:01,840
any little injury will heal right up.

19
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:02,719
If it weren't for Xiaojiu...

20
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:07,640
If Xiaojiu hadn't insisted
that you treat me,

21
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,719
would we had to hide in here
just to eat hot pot?

22
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:12,159
She's only acting this way
because she cares.

23
00:01:12,159 --> 00:01:12,560
Master,

24
00:01:12,799 --> 00:01:14,120
you should feel lucky

25
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:16,120
to have a kindhearted girl

26
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,640
like Xiaojiu by your side.

27
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,480
I do. I do.

28
00:01:24,159 --> 00:01:25,359
Why does it smell

29
00:01:25,359 --> 00:01:28,159
like spicy hot pot in there?

30
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,239
Extra-spicy beef tallow.

31
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:37,000
X-Xiaojiu...

32
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,719
Mr. Tang gave me strict orders.

33
00:01:39,159 --> 00:01:40,840
No one goes in

34
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,959
while he's treating Dasheng.

35
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,079
You have to trust him.

36
00:01:43,079 --> 00:01:43,959
This is Mr. Tang we're talking about.

37
00:01:43,959 --> 00:01:45,439
He's the Divine Healer.

38
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:46,599
With him treating Dasheng,

39
00:01:46,599 --> 00:01:48,239
what is there to worry about?

40
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:50,599
I'll just take a look.

41
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,400
No, wait...

42
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:55,200
Xiaojiu, don't make this hard for me.

43
00:01:55,439 --> 00:01:56,519
Mr. Tang is in there.

44
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,120
Fiery...

45
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:12,560
Master, let me remind you.

46
00:02:12,719 --> 00:02:14,639
You got away with
a flesh wound this time,

47
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:16,919
but you won't always be so lucky.

48
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,439
Don't forget,

49
00:02:18,439 --> 00:02:19,960
you were born with sealed meridians.

50
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,120
And now you've made

51
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,560
an enemy of the Demon Sect.

52
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,680
You need to be much more careful
from now on.

53
00:02:26,439 --> 00:02:30,159
Before I left the sect,

54
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:31,680
my master warned me again and again

55
00:02:31,759 --> 00:02:32,879
to return to the sect
before my 20th birthday.

56
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:35,719
I only have

57
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:37,599
seven days left.

58
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:42,919
Changsheng, Xiaojiu and I
are leaving Gusu tomorrow.

59
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,919
No matter how powerful they are,

60
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:47,240
they can't do a thing
if they don't know where I am.

61
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:49,159
That's for the best.

62
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:50,680
Master,

63
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:53,680
can I take a look at your soul jade?

64
00:03:03,199 --> 00:03:06,520
Master, this soul jade
is no ordinary treasure.

65
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:10,639
The spiritual power inside it
is overwhelming.

66
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:12,639
Only someone who shares
its owner's bloodline

67
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:15,240
could control it.

68
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:19,560
So that's what happened.

69
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,000
Last time I fought

70
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,360
the Demon Sect,

71
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:25,479
a powerful spiritual force

72
00:03:25,479 --> 00:03:27,960
suddenly surged through my meridians

73
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,639
and instantly boosted my cultivation.

74
00:03:30,479 --> 00:03:32,000
I couldn't understand it at the time.

75
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:35,120
So the soul jade
was secretly helping me.

76
00:03:37,319 --> 00:03:39,759
But who could have put

77
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,599
such overwhelming power into it?

78
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:45,879
Whoever infused this soul jade
with spiritual power

79
00:03:45,879 --> 00:03:47,400
is no ordinary martial artist.

80
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:51,159
His cultivation has already reached
the Immortal Realm.

81
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,879
Even the Four Grandmasters alive today

82
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:55,479
wouldn't come close.

83
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,280
My master said

84
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,960
my father left it to me.

85
00:04:01,159 --> 00:04:02,879
Could my father really
have been stronger

86
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:06,680
than the Four Grandmasters?

87
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:08,840
Who's there?

88
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,560
Xiaojiu?

89
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:18,920
Are you okay?

90
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,000
Are you hurt?

91
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,720
Mr. Tang.

92
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:39,399
Xiaojiu.

93
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:45,759
So this is
the special treatment you mentioned?

94
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,279
Master,

95
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:50,279
I just remembered

96
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,879
my wife's in labor!

97
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:52,959
It's an emergency.

98
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:53,959
I have to go!

99
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,319
Get back here, you weasel!

100
00:04:55,319 --> 00:04:56,360
Dasheng!

101
00:04:58,199 --> 00:04:59,959
You ingrate!

102
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:17,560
The Tianji Armor?

103
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,600
Why are you giving me this?

104
00:05:19,199 --> 00:05:21,959
Put it on so you don't get hurt.

105
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,600
Stop arguing.

106
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,000
(Baicao House)

107
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:31,439
No wonder he's the Divine Healer.

108
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:33,800
Even his treatments
shake the whole place.

109
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:50,199
(Besides, my heart already
belongs to someone else.)

110
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:59,120
Miss, what's wrong?

111
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,199
I don't know.

112
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:06,319
I just feel empty inside,

113
00:06:06,959 --> 00:06:08,480
like something's missing.

114
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,839
Miss...

115
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,439
A restless mind throws

116
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,360
the body and spirit off balance.

117
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:16,480
That's dangerous for a martial artist.

118
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:19,319
Master, you're back.

119
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:20,879
Qingyao,

120
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:23,959
have you fallen for Peng Dasheng?

121
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,519
I...

122
00:06:31,439 --> 00:06:34,079
What is love that makes us vow

123
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:36,480
to live and die for it?

124
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,319
Once,

125
00:06:39,319 --> 00:06:42,000
I had true love right in front of me,

126
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,720
but I didn't cherish it.

127
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:48,959
Only after I lost it did I understand
how painful regret could be.

128
00:06:48,959 --> 00:06:52,000
Nothing in this world hurts more.

129
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:55,519
Master, what are you doing up there?

130
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,360
Weren't you and your wife

131
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,800
betrothed before birth?

132
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,319
The past

133
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:08,879
is best left alone.

134
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:16,399
Master, are you telling me
to give up on him?

135
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:18,199
I didn't say that.

136
00:07:18,519 --> 00:07:19,319
By the way,

137
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:21,040
I asked you to recruit Peng Dasheng

138
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:23,000
to help us fight the Demon Sect.

139
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,439
How did it go?

140
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,759
He refused.

141
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:32,560
Miss Duan,
I'm truly sorry, but I can't help.

142
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:33,759
Why not?

143
00:07:33,839 --> 00:07:35,120
To be honest,

144
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,639
ever since I was little,

145
00:07:36,639 --> 00:07:37,920
my master has told me
I was born with sealed meridians

146
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,040
and wasn't meant to live long.

147
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:42,360
See these pills?
My master gave them to me.

148
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:43,839
I need them every day
just to stay alive.

149
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,680
Without them, I'd already be dead.

150
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,120
So I really can't help you

151
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,399
fight the Demon Sect.

152
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,639
I can't even fight my own fate.

153
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,360
Born with sealed meridians...

154
00:07:55,399 --> 00:07:56,199
Miss Duan,

155
00:07:57,199 --> 00:07:58,759
I'm heading back to my sect tomorrow.

156
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:00,040
It's a long road ahead.

157
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,519
Take care.

158
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:11,000
In that case,

159
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:13,120
I won't push it.

160
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,560
Master,

161
00:08:14,759 --> 00:08:16,480
what do we do now?

162
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,639
The Demon Sect is running rampant,

163
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,720
all because of Master Baiyi.

164
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:26,199
He knows the martial world's
inner workings inside out.

165
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:29,279
He's no ordinary man.

166
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:31,920
You think

167
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,120
Master Baiyi may be

168
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,679
from the martial world?

169
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:38,600
I've found his trail.

170
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:41,039
Once I confirm who he really is,

171
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:43,279
I can rally the entire martial world

172
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:44,200
against him.

173
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:45,720
I'm coming with you.

174
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:47,519
I'm tracking him.

175
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:49,039
The fewer who know, the better.

176
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,720
With my cultivation,

177
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,039
I can take care of myself.

178
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:58,200
Then please be careful, Master.

179
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:01,759
(Qingyao.)

180
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:04,320
(If anything happens to me,)

181
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:06,399
(protect the Wudu Sect.)

182
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:09,440
(Protect our home.)

183
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:33,080
I am Song Qingbo,
Netherworld Deputy Envoy.

184
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,480
Greetings, Demon Envoys.

185
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,440
Mr. Song.

186
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:38,559
How did the task

187
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:40,279
I gave you go?

188
00:09:40,279 --> 00:09:41,679
I went to Huxiao Manor.

189
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:43,399
Lin Dun agreed to work with us.

190
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:51,559
Master gave you this
Five Minerals Powder as a reward.

191
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,080
Catch it.

192
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,960
As long as you do as you're told,

193
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:04,240
you can have all
the Five Minerals Powder you want.

194
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,320
I won't fail you,

195
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,840
even if it costs me my life.

196
00:10:16,300 --> 00:10:19,140
(Hero's Summons)

197
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:23,799
Master,

198
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,879
Miss Duan took some people
to Taiping Villa outside the city.

199
00:10:28,679 --> 00:10:30,000
What is she doing there?

200
00:10:30,799 --> 00:10:32,679
Hongxiu said she went

201
00:10:32,679 --> 00:10:34,879
to the countryside to clear her head.

202
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:41,720
Very well.

203
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,960
She's been troubled lately.

204
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,759
A little time away might do her good.

205
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:46,919
Here.

206
00:10:47,519 --> 00:10:50,360
Make exact copies of this

207
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:53,000
and send them by the fastest courier
to every sect leader.

208
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:56,000
Master, are you calling
a Martial Arts Assembly?

209
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,879
The Demon Sect is running rampant,

210
00:10:58,320 --> 00:11:01,000
and Master Baiyi has resurfaced,

211
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,440
throwing the realm into chaos.

212
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,519
It's time to unite the martial world

213
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:07,080
and wipe out the Demon Sect.

214
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:07,720
Yes, Master.

215
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,720
I'll see to it at once.

216
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:25,559
Miss,

217
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,360
you've been drinking for two hours.

218
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:29,240
You'll hurt yourself if you keep going.

219
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:31,120
Hongxiu,

220
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:34,360
do you think I'm vain

221
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,559
and heartless too?

222
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,679
Of course not.

223
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,440
Others may not understand,

224
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,240
but I do.

225
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,799
You didn't break off the engagement

226
00:11:41,799 --> 00:11:43,399
out of vanity.

227
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:54,000
My mother died when I was young.

228
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:57,039
Father raised me alone.

229
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:02,200
Back then, the Murong family
had little power.

230
00:12:02,399 --> 00:12:04,240
Whenever people treated him badly,

231
00:12:04,759 --> 00:12:06,639
he'd come home and force a smile.

232
00:12:07,559 --> 00:12:09,279
I couldn't wait to grow up

233
00:12:10,799 --> 00:12:12,399
so I could help carry his burden.

234
00:12:13,879 --> 00:12:15,320
But as a woman,

235
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:20,039
what else could I do

236
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:22,200
but marry for my family's sake?

237
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:29,799
Miss,

238
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:32,039
the engagement is over.

239
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:34,279
We'll find you the right man.

240
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:35,919
Why let

241
00:12:35,919 --> 00:12:38,039
Peng Dasheng's words upset you?

242
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,399
You're right.

243
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:43,879
Why am I letting a stranger's words

244
00:12:43,879 --> 00:12:45,200
get to me?

245
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,159
Miss, run!

246
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:13,480
Miss, go!

247
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:14,879
Hongxiu!

248
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:27,120
Such a pretty young woman.

249
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:31,279
If I had a face like yours,

250
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:33,559
men would line up to let me drain

251
00:13:33,559 --> 00:13:36,399
their life force.

252
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:38,159
Kill me,

253
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:40,360
and my father will never
let you get away with it.

254
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:44,399
A helpless little thing like you

255
00:13:44,879 --> 00:13:46,759
dares threaten me?

256
00:13:50,919 --> 00:13:54,440
The Demon Sect's Bone-Eroding Poison
is already in your system.

257
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,519
Within three days,

258
00:13:56,879 --> 00:14:01,279
your flesh will melt
into a pool of blood.

259
00:14:01,519 --> 00:14:04,039
That Peng Dasheng
you can't stop thinking about,

260
00:14:04,399 --> 00:14:08,360
do you think he'll come
see you one last time?

261
00:14:16,519 --> 00:14:17,840
You handle

262
00:14:18,679 --> 00:14:20,480
the rest.

263
00:14:33,740 --> 00:14:34,220
♪Come on♪

264
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:39,420
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

265
00:14:41,380 --> 00:14:44,340
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

266
00:14:44,620 --> 00:14:47,540
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

267
00:14:47,780 --> 00:14:50,620
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

268
00:14:51,020 --> 00:14:53,620
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

269
00:14:54,140 --> 00:14:57,100
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

270
00:14:57,340 --> 00:15:00,340
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

271
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:03,420
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

272
00:15:03,580 --> 00:15:06,340
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

273
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:10,220
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

274
00:15:10,260 --> 00:15:13,260
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

275
00:15:13,300 --> 00:15:18,940
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

276
00:15:19,340 --> 00:15:21,380
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

277
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:24,460
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

278
00:15:25,180 --> 00:15:27,580
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

279
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:31,380
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

280
00:15:31,980 --> 00:15:34,100
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

281
00:15:35,020 --> 00:15:37,140
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

282
00:15:37,300 --> 00:15:40,580
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

283
00:15:40,620 --> 00:15:44,900
♪I am my own king♪

284
00:15:57,980 --> 00:15:59,540
♪I emerge into the world♪

285
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:01,300
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

286
00:16:01,300 --> 00:16:02,660
♪My pride is my trump card♪

287
00:16:02,660 --> 00:16:04,460
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

288
00:16:04,460 --> 00:16:05,860
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

289
00:16:05,860 --> 00:16:07,620
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

290
00:16:07,620 --> 00:16:09,140
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

291
00:16:09,140 --> 00:16:10,860
♪I dare to break every rule♪

292
00:16:10,860 --> 00:16:12,180
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

293
00:16:12,180 --> 00:16:14,020
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

294
00:16:14,020 --> 00:16:15,260
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

295
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:17,500
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

296
00:16:17,500 --> 00:16:19,020
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

297
00:16:19,020 --> 00:16:20,620
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

298
00:16:20,620 --> 00:16:22,220
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

299
00:16:22,220 --> 00:16:23,940
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

300
00:16:23,940 --> 00:16:25,660
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

301
00:16:25,660 --> 00:16:27,020
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

302
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:28,660
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

303
00:16:28,660 --> 00:16:30,140
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

304
00:16:30,140 --> 00:16:31,860
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

305
00:16:31,860 --> 00:16:33,460
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

306
00:16:33,460 --> 00:16:35,020
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

307
00:16:35,020 --> 00:16:39,340
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

308
00:16:39,340 --> 00:16:41,500
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

309
00:16:41,500 --> 00:16:44,100
♪Let me write the legend♪

310
00:16:48,980 --> 00:16:51,540
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

311
00:16:51,540 --> 00:16:54,860
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

312
00:16:54,860 --> 00:16:57,340
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

313
00:16:57,340 --> 00:17:01,420
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

314
00:17:01,780 --> 00:17:04,380
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

315
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:06,860
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

316
00:17:06,860 --> 00:17:09,900
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

317
00:17:09,900 --> 00:17:14,940
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
